0.1.name: wordpress/wp-e-commerce-bring-fraktguide
0.1.description:
This is a shipping module for WP e-Commerce. It uses the Bring Fraktguide XML API to get shipping quotes.

It will get accurate prices based on delivery postcode, weight, length, width, height and volume.

The plugin only supports WP e-Commerce 3.8 and later.
